StratmasClient.communication
Class StratmasMessageEvent

java.lang.Object
  java.util.EventObject
      StratmasClient.communication.StratmasMessageEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class StratmasMessageEvent
extends EventObject

This class represents the events that may be sent by a StratmasMessage to indicate the progress of the message. Events are currently sent when the message is sent to the server, when the client has received the answer and when the answer is handled or when something has gone wrong.
